API_PKC KAT files are generated per parameter set by KAT_KEM executable:
output/KAT_KEM_Venom-128.txt
output/KAT_KEM_Venom-192.txt
output/KAT_KEM_Venom-256.txt
output/KAT_KEM_Venom-384.txt
output/KAT_KEM_Venom-512.txt

After generation, copy into API_PKC/Test_Vectors/ for packaging.
Generated KAT files are not committed in this repository stage.

Note:
- Original template directory API_PKC/Test_Vector is preserved unchanged.
- API_PKC/Test_Vectors is the Venom migration output-collection location.
